guys got together over drinks at Joe &amp; Rose's to apply their combined creative talents toward the development of new and interesting ways to meet women. The result of this weighty conference was the New York Advertising Co-Ed Softball league.<\/p>\n<\/span><\/div>\n<div id=\"mylink\"><span class=\"tk-league-gothic\"><a href=\"\/archive\/nyacsl-2011\/10a-nyacsl-2012-VIEWS-PATCH-APPLICATION-2\/node\/61\">READ MORE ABOUT OUR LEAGUE<\/a>, <a href=\"\/archive\/nyacsl-2011\/10a-nyacsl-2012-VIEWS-PATCH-APPLICATION-2\/contact\">CONTACT US<\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div><\/a><\/span>  <\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"views_slideshow_cycle_div_slideshow_d7-page_1_2\" class=\"views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row views_slideshow_cycle_slide views_slideshow_slide views-row-3 views_slideshow_cycle_hidden views-row-odd\">\n  <div class=\"views-slideshow-cycle-main-frame-row-item views-row views-row-0 views-row-first views-row-odd\">\n    \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-field-slideshow-image\">        <div class=\"field-content\"><img src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/archive\/nyacsl-2011\/10a-nyacsl-2012-VIEWS-PATCH-APPLICATION-2\/sites\/default\/files\/fields.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/div>  <\/div>  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-title\">        <span class=\"field-content\"><a href=\"\/archive\/nyacsl-2011\/10a-nyacsl-2012-VIEWS-PATCH-APPLICATION-2\/node\/1323\"><div id=\"transparency\"><\/div>\n<div id=\"mycontent\">\n<span class=\"tk-league-gothic\">OUR BRAND NEW FIELDS<\/span>\n<div id=\"myteaser\"><span class=\"tk-junction\"><p>Since its inception, the NYACSL has played mostly all of its games on Ward's Island. However, in August 2007, the Randall's Island Sports Foundation (RISF) and the City undertook a project to reconfigure and rebuild over 60 athletic playing fields on Randall\u2019s Island. The NYACSL is a long-time affiliate of the RISF and beginning this year, we now play all regular and post-season games on these newly rebuilt fields.<\/p>\n<\/span><\/div>\n<div id=\"mylink\"><span
